<p>
  <h1>Scram!</h1>
  <h3>It's time to go...</h3>
  <p>Do you feel the need to travel, but don't have the means? </p>
  <p>Do you have a vision to share, but can't get there? </p>
  <p>Through Scram, we offer youth the opportunity to travel with grants provided by the community.<br> Look at our Submissions page.<br>If you are a young person with a mission, please sign up and share a video essay about where you want to go and what volunteer opportunity you are interested in.  Your submission will be live for one month.<br>Share your submission via social media, with your friends, family and colleagues.<br>Get votes! Get Donations!<br>The youth with the most votes will receive the donations for that month.</p>
